71
00:05:36,976 --> 00:05:38,737
Okay, no flashes anymore.

72
00:05:39,278 --> 00:05:43,760
Then in this case, CFF is at 30 hertz.

73
00:05:44,281 --> 00:05:47,002
That means when the flashes increase,

74
