302
00:26:18,704 --> 00:26:22,045
When designing new maps, adding new elements,

303
00:26:22,855 --> 00:26:24,896
or making any changes to your game,

304
00:26:25,637 --> 00:26:29,379
you can use A-B testing to identify elements

305
00:26:29,919 --> 00:26:34,382
that might cause visual fatigue and try to reduce its impact.

306
00:26:35,823 --> 00:26:40,146
As I explained earlier, CFF and contrast sensitivity

307
00:26:40,386 --> 00:26:44,509
